31
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,880
You can see that we have started with the entity.

32
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:21,620
In our case, this will be the order aggregate that include domain events list.

33
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:27,350
So whenever any order created this will be triggered order created, domain event and adding this domain

34
00:02:27,350 --> 00:02:30,350
event into list of the domain events into the aggregate.

35
00:02:30,350 --> 00:02:33,350
And after that there is a separate event dispatcher.

36
00:02:33,350 --> 00:02:39,710
In our case this will be using Entity Framework code save change interceptor in order to dispatch these

37
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:41,750
